      <textAnnotation id="sid-5D5F56E9-6C11-4385-83E2-AFDCA13489D2" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Once the material has been defined as non-conforming, disposition (send) it to the appropriate reject/non-conforming warehouse with the appropriate 'Rejected Material' tags. Identify potential corrective action options including in-house rework/repair, return to supplier, waiver issuance, send to scrap, etc. Analyze the results of the inspection and determine a use for the unacceptable received material.
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-E0DF2454-3A10-4F41-B230-11B499D9F891" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Offline Communication</text>
      </textAnnotation>
